# Stack: FastAPI Baller backend

## Layout (repo)

- `backend/app/main.py` — app factory, CORS, routers
- `backend/app/routers/` — `auth`, `courts`, `profiles`, `uploads`
- `backend/app/security/` — JWT, Argon2
- `backend/migrations/` — SQL schema
- `docker-compose.yml` (repo root)

## Local

```powershell
copy backend\.env.example .env
docker compose up -d --build
```

Docs: `http://localhost:8000/docs`

## Env (production)

- `DATABASE_URL`, `JWT_SECRET`, `ENVIRONMENT`, `CORS_ORIGINS`
- `B2_KEY_ID`, `B2_APP_KEY`, `B2_BUCKET`, `B2_ENDPOINT`, `B2_REGION`

## Flutter

```text
--dart-define=API_BASE_URL=https://api.example.com
--dart-define=USE_LEGACY_SUPABASE=false
```

## Not in this stack

- Supabase Auth / RLS / Realtime (legacy until cutover)
- MinIO on VPS (use B2)


